---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Contact" description="Schedule a call or send a message — let's talk about your systems.">

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="eyebrow">Contact</div>
      <h1>Let's talk about<br /><span class="accent">your systems.</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">No pitch deck. A 30-minute conversation about what your team is working on and whether Woodhead Tech can help.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="contact-grid">

        <div class="contact-main">
          <div class="card calendly-card">
            <div class="card-label">Schedule a call</div>
            <p class="card-desc">
              Pick a time that works for you. First call is always free — 30 minutes, no obligation.
            </p>
            <!-- Replace the href below with your Calendly link -->
            <a
              href="https://cal.com/brandon-woodward-3nlfbd"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="btn btn-primary calendly-btn"
            >
              Open Scheduling Calendar →
            </a>
            <p class="calendly-note">Opens Cal.com in a new tab</p>
          </div>

          <div class="or-divider">
            <span>or reach out directly</span>
          </div>

          <div class="card email-card">
            <div class="card-label">Email</div>
            <a href="mailto:brandon@woodhead.tech" class="email-link">brandon@woodhead.tech</a>
            <p class="email-note">Response within 24 hours on business days.</p>

            <div class="card-label" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">Phone & WhatsApp</div>
            <a href="tel:+14253442942" class="email-link">(425) 344-2942</a>
            <p class="email-note">Call, text, or <a href="https://wa.me/14253442942" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #25D366; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: underline;">WhatsApp</a>. Business hours preferred.</p>

            <div class="what-to-include">
              <div class="wti-label">Helpful to include</div>
              <ul>
                <li>What your team is building or trying to automate</li>
                <li>Approximate team size and engineering stack</li>
                <li>What you've already tried</li>
                <li>Your timeline and urgency</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-sidebar">
          <div class="card sidebar-info">
            <div class="info-label">What happens next</div>
            <div class="steps">
              <div class="step">
                <div class="step-num">1</div>
                <div class="step-text">
                  <strong>30-min intro call</strong>
                  <p>We talk about your systems, your team's pain, and whether the engagement makes sense.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="step">
                <div class="step-num">2</div>
                <div class="step-text">
                  <strong>Scope or proposal</strong>
                  <p>If there's a fit, Woodhead Tech sends a written scope document with a fixed price and timeline.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="step">
                <div class="step-num">3</div>
                <div class="step-text">
                  <strong>We start</strong>
                  <p>50% upfront, work begins. No retainer, no ongoing fees unless that's what we agreed.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card sidebar-info" style="margin-top: 1.25rem;">
            <div class="info-label">Good fit if...</div>
            <ul class="fit-list">
              <li>Your team has 10–200 engineers</li>
              <li>You have a specific automation problem or AI integration in mind</li>
              <li>You want architecture expertise, not a vendor</li>
              <li>You can execute once the architecture is designed</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="info-label" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">Not a fit if...</div>
            <ul class="fit-list not-fit">
              <li>You need a full-time embedded contractor</li>
              <li>The problem is still undefined ("we should do something with AI")</li>
              <li>You need a large team or agency deliverable</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: 5rem 0 3.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .page-hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); margin-bottom: 1rem; }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 480px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Grid */
  .contact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* Calendly card */
  .card-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .card-desc { color: var(--dim); font-size: 0.92rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.6; }

  .calendly-btn { font-size: 1rem; padding: 0.85rem 1.75rem; }

  .calendly-note {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  /* Divider */
  .or-divider {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .or-divider::before,
  .or-divider::after {
    content: '';
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
  }

  /* Email card */
  .email-link {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .email-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  .email-note { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }

  .what-to-include { margin-top: 1.5rem; padding-top: 1.5rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }

  .wti-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .what-to-include ul { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }

  .what-to-include li {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--dim);
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .what-to-include li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  /* Sidebar */
  .info-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  /* Steps */
  .steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.25rem; }

  .step { display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start; }

  .step-num {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    background: rgba(181, 85, 26, 0.10);
    border: 1px solid rgba(181, 85, 26, 0.28);
    color: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .step-text strong { display: block; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }

  .step-text p { font-size: 0.83rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; }

  /* Fit list */
  .fit-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }

  .fit-list li {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--dim);
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .fit-list li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  .fit-list.not-fit li::before {
    content: '✗';
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .fit-list.not-fit li { color: var(--muted); }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
